# Gurobi warm-start parameters — loaded by the gtopt Gurobi backend (via
# GRBreadparams) as a sibling of the case's main gurobi.prm when
# SolverOptions::advanced_basis is active (SDDP aperture warm-start /
# fixed-MILP dual recovery).  Mirrors cplex_warmstart.prm.
#   Method 0   primal simplex — warm-starts off the resident VBasis/CBasis
#              (Method 1 = dual simplex; barrier=2 cannot warm-start).
#   Presolve 0 keep presolve from disturbing the reused basis.
Method 0
Presolve 0
